snippet.title: Heli Attack 2 11245300 points and gameplay
snippet.description: Who else remembers this very, very fun game from Miniclip.com? Developed in 2003, i do remember i have been playing it in the early and late 2000's, that was 15 years ago, a shame that time goes by so quickly!
